Package: dPCP
Title: Digital PCR Cluster Predictor: a flexible and sensitive algorithm for 
        the automated analysis of multiplex digital PCR data
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Alfonso", family = "De Falco",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                    email = "alfonso.defalco@lns.etat.lu"),
            person(given = "Daniel", family = "Stieber", role = c("ctb")),
            person(given = "Michel", family = "Mittelbronn", role = c("ctb")))
Description: digital PCR Cluster Predictor is an algorithm for the automated
        clustering of digital PCR data. dPCP can cluster data with up to 4 
        targets and calculate their concentration.
        The details about input and data parameters are available in the 
        vignette. 
License: Artistic-2.0
